clipboard_import_dialog_title: Import spreadsheet data as child tasks to __task_or_project_name__
clipboard_import_duplicate_field: More than 1 column is selected as __field__
clipboard_import_column_number_mismatch: Mismatch in number of columns on different rows. Import aborted.
clipboard_import_invalid_option_value: Invalid __field__ value __val__ in line __line__ - not a valid option. Import aborted.
clipboard_import_value_should_be_number: Invalid value __val__ in line __line__ - should be a number. Import aborted.
clipboard_import_value_out_of_range: Invalid __field__ value __val__ in line __line__ (must be between __min__ and __max__). Import aborted.
clipboard_import_invalid_date_format: Invalid date format in line __line__. Import aborted.
clipboard_import_invalid_indent: Invalid indentation at line __line__ - inconsistent indentation.
clipboard_import_milestone_can_only_have: Task __task__ at line __line__ is a milestone, it can only have the same Start Date and End Date.
clipboard_import_too_many_rows: Too many rows, you may copy up to __limit__ rows.
clipboard_import_cant_find_tabular_data: Can't find tabular information in clipboard.
clipboard_import_placeholder_msg:
Copy content from your spreadsheet and paste it here to create tasks.
The first column is regarded as the Subject.
clipboard_import_user_not_found: User not found in the current JustDo, invite the user first.
